#. Tag: title
#: details-institutions.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Institutions"
msgstr "Institucije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-institutions.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Institutions in &kmymoney; serve as a way to group accounts. They are most "
"commonly financial institutions like banks and brokerage firms, but they can "
"be anything you want, such as <quote>Self</quote>, to hold accounts for the "
"cash in your pocket and any other assets not actually help by a financial "
"institution, or <quote>Stores</quote>, to group all your credit card and "
"other accounts with retail stores."
msgstr ""
"Institucije v &kmymoney; služijo kot način združevanja računov. Najpogosteje "
"so to finančne institucije, kot so banke in borznoposredniške družbe, lahko "
"pa so karkoli želite, na primer <quote>Jaz</quote>, da ima račune za "
"gotovino v vašem žepu in vsa druga sredstva, kjer vam dejansko ne pomaga "
"institucija ali <quote>Trgovine</quote>, da združite vse svoje kreditne "
"kartice in druge račune maloprodajnih trgovin."

#. Tag: title
#: details-institutions.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "Institutions View"
msgstr "Pogled institucij"

#. Tag: para
#: details-institutions.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Institutions View provides a summary of all the accounts grouped under "
"their respective institutions. The list of accounts under any institution "
"can be expanded or collapsed by clicking on the arrow to the left of the "
"institution name. The last listed institution is \"Accounts with no "
"institution assigned.\""
msgstr ""
"Pogled institucij nudi povzetek vseh računov, združenih v ustreznih "
"institucijah. Seznam računov pri kateri koli instituciji lahko razširite ali "
"strnete s klikom na puščico levo od imena institucije. Zadnja navedena "
"institucija je \"Računi brez dodeljene institucije.\""

#. Tag: para
#: details-institutions.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Institutions View displays several columns, showing information about "
"the account. It also shows the total value of all accounts in each "
"institution. You can select which columns are shown by right-clicking on any "
"column heading and selecting or unselecting the checkbox next to the name of "
"the column."
msgstr ""
"Pogled institucij prikazuje več stolpcev, ki prikazujejo informacije o "
"računu. Prikazuje tudi skupno vrednost vseh računov v vsaki instituciji. "
"Izberete lahko, kateri stolpci so prikazani, tako da z desno miškino tipko "
"kliknete naslov katerega koli stolpca in izberete ali počistite potrditveno "
"polje poleg imena stolpca."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-institutions.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>institution view</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>pogled institucij</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-institutions.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>institution view</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>pogled institucij</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: details-institutions.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Ime"

#. Tag: para
#: details-institutions.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The name of the institution or account. This column is always displayed."
msgstr "Ime institucije ali računa. Ta stolpec je vedno prikazan."

#. Tag: term
#: details-institutions.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "Balance"
msgstr "Stanje"

#. Tag: para
#: details-institutions.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The current balance of the account. No value is displayed for institutions."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno stanje na računu. Za institucije ni prikazane nobene vrednosti."

#. Tag: term
#: details-institutions.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Total Value"
msgstr "Skupna vrednost"

#. Tag: para
#: details-institutions.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For accounts, this is the same value as the balance. For Institutions, this "
"is the total of the balances for all accounts in that institution."
msgstr ""
"Za račune je to enaka vrednosti kot stanje. Za institucije je to vsota stanj "
"za vse račune v tej instituciji."

#. Tag: term
#: details-institutions.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "IBAN"
msgstr "IBAN"

#. Tag: para
#: details-institutions.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <acronym><ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"International_Bank_Account_Number\">IBAN</ulink> </acronym> (International "
"Bank Account Number) is shown if there is a value entered in the appropriate "
"field on the account information dialog."
msgstr ""
"<acronym><ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"International_Bank_Account_Number\">IBAN</ulink> </acronym> (mednarodna "
"številka bančnega računa) je prikazana, če vnesena je v ustrezno polje v "
"pogovornem oknu s podatki o računu."

#. Tag: term
#: details-institutions.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bank Code"
msgstr "Koda banke"

#. Tag: para
#: details-institutions.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bank_code\">Bank Code</"
"ulink>. This identifier is formatted and used differently in different "
"countries. It is known as the routing or routing transit number in the US "
"and as the sort code in the UK. It is not currently used by &kmymoney;."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bank_code\">Koda banke</ulink>. "
"Ta identifikator je v različnih državah različno oblikovan in uporabljen. "
"Znana je kot usmerjevalna ali tranzitna številka v ZDA in kot razvrstitvena "
"koda v Združenem kraljestvu. &kmymoney; ga trenutno ne uporablja."

#. Tag: term
#: details-institutions.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "SWIFT/BIC"
msgstr "SWIFT/BIC"

#. Tag: para
#: details-institutions.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <acronym><ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_9362\">SWIFT/"
"BIC</ulink></acronym> (Society for Worldwide Interbank Financial "
"Telecommunication/Business Identifier Code)"
msgstr ""
"<acronym><ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_9362\">SWIFT/BIC</"
"ulink></acronym> (Society for Worldwide Interbank Financial "
"Telecommunication/Business Identifier Code)"

#. Tag: title
#: details-institutions.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Institution Options"
msgstr "Možnosti institucije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-institutions.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right-clicking an institution name brings up an Institution Options menu, "
"providing you with several choices. Selecting <guimenuitem>New Institution..."
"</guimenuitem> opens the New Institution Dialog, where you can enter all the "
"necessary information to create a new institution. Selecting "
"<guimenuitem>Edit Institution...</guimenuitem> brings up an editable window "
"where you can change the institution details. Selecting <guimenuitem>Delete "
"Institution</guimenuitem> completely removes the institution from the data "
"file. Any accounts associated with that institution will remain, but without "
"being associated with any institution. Selecting <guimenuitem>New account..."
"</guimenuitem> steps you through the new account process, which is described "
"in more detail in the next section."
msgstr ""
"Če z desno miškino tipko kliknete ime institucije, se odpre meni z možnostmi "
"institucije, ki vam ponuja več možnosti. Če izberete <guimenuitem>Nova "
"institucija ...</guimenuitem>, se odpre pogovorno okno Nova institucija, "
"kjer lahko vnesete vse potrebne informacije za ustvarjanje nove institucije. "
"Če izberete <guimenuitem>Urejanje institucije...</guimenuitem>, se prikaže "
"okno, ki ga je mogoče urejati, kjer lahko spremenite podrobnosti "
"institucije. Če izberete <guimenuitem>Izbriši institucijo</guimenuitem>, "
"institucijo popolnoma odstranite iz podatkovne datoteke. Vsi računi, "
"povezani s to institucijo, bodo ostali, vendar ne bodo povezani z nobeno "
"institucijo. Če izberete <guimenuitem>Nov račun...</guimenuitem>, vas vodi "
"skozi postopek novega računa, ki je podrobneje opisan v naslednjem razdelku."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-institutions.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>institution options sub-menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>podmeni z možnostmi institucije</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-institutions.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>institution options sub-menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>podmeni z možnostmi institucije</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: details-institutions.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Institution"
msgstr "Nova institucija"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-institutions.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>new institution</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>nova institucija</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-institutions.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new institution</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>nova institucija</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-institutions.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You must have a file open before you can create a new institution. If you do "
"not have an existing file, you will need to <link linkend=\"firsttime.newfile"
"\">create one</link>."
msgstr ""
"Preden lahko ustvarite novo ustanovo, morate imeti odprto datoteko. Če še "
"nimate obstoječe datoteke, jo boste morali <link linkend=\"firsttime.newfile"
"\">ustvariti</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-institutions.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only the name is required in the New Institution Dialog, all other fields "
"are optional. As with the personal information dialog, this data is not "
"currently used by &kmymoney;, but some items may be required by future "
"releases for certain features. In particular, the <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Bank_code\">Bank Code</ulink> and the <acronym> <ulink "
"url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_9362\">BIC (Bank Identifier Code)</"
"ulink></acronym> will be required for online banking, although this may "
"depend on the country your bank is in."
msgstr ""
"V pogovornem oknu za novo institucijo je potrebno samo ime, vsa druga polja "
"so neobvezna. Tako kot pri pogovornem oknu z osebnimi podatki, &kmymoney; "
"teh podatkov trenutno ne uporablja, vendar bodo nekateri elementi morda "
"potrebni v prihodnjih izdajah za nekatere funkcije. Zlasti <ulink url="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bank_code\">koda banke</ulink> in <acronym> "
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/ wiki/ISO_9362\">BIC (bančna "
"identifikacijska koda)</ulink></acronym> bo potreben za spletno bančništvo, "
"čeprav je to lahko odvisno od države, v kateri je vaša banka v."

#. Tag: title
#: details-institutions.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account Options"
msgstr "Možnosti računa"

#. Tag: para
#: details-institutions.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The options discussed above refer to the institutions listed in the "
"Institutions View. Most of the rows in this view are accounts. Right-"
"clicking an account name brings up an Account Options menu. The entries and "
"details for this menu are discussed at the end of the <link linkend="
"\"details.accounts.options\">Accounts Chapter</link>."
msgstr ""
"Zgoraj obravnavane možnosti se nanašajo na institucije, navedene v Pogledu "
"institucij. Večina vrstic v tem pogledu so računi. Z desnim klikom na ime "
"računa se odpre meni z možnostmi računa. Vnosi in podrobnosti za ta meni so "
"obravnavani na koncu <link linkend=\"details.accounts.options\">poglavja o "
"računih</link>."

